node.text:
Visit @SculptMovements 💕 for workouts, routine, and everythin else you eed to become fit! .
Treino de MMI com 01. Agachamento máquina 15/12/10 + drop com extensora 4 x 4 / 4x3 / 4x2 /4x 1 aumentando a carga ( 1 série ) 
1 x 10 com pico de contração em cima + 10 saindo da inércia 
1 x 10 com excêntrica lenta + 10 concêntrica lenta + 10 
02. Stiff 3 x 15 + bom dia 10 
03. Flexora 9 x 6 alternando a carga entre leva e pesado 
1 x 30 curtas + 10 isometria + 12 
1 x unilateral 8 /7/6 até zerar sem intervalo 
04. Flexora em pé 3 x 12 parando no meio + glúteo no cabo 3 x 12 
Panturrilhas sempre 😅
Macacão @santtaloren
.
.
.

node.text:
Caption this 👀
cc: @catjesse

SWIPE FOR HARDCORE FULL-BODY WORKOUT💪🏽

Happy Friday friennnnn 🥳

Bringing you the last workout for this week. Today we are focusing of targeting each and every muscle group.

To make it even sweeter, you can do all of these exercises using only a pair of Dumbbells.

Pro Tip: Focus on isolating the muscles you are targeting with each exercise to get the most out of each rep and exercise.

SAVE⚡️ LIKE⚡️ SHARE⚡️ EXECUTE

METHOD: Perform each exercise for 10 reps  for a total of 3 sets!

Tag a friend to join in on the sweat💦

Credit @jenna.deleon

BUDDY WORKOUT 👯‍♀️❤️‍🔥 TAG your babes and challenge them to workout together ⬇️👀 See you tomorrow at 8:00am EST for a booty and leg workout 🔥 Method: repeat each exercise 3 times - 45sec ON 10sec OFF

Save, share and let’s do it sis 👊🏼 

BUDDY WORKOUT 👯‍♀️❤️‍🔥 Etiqueta a tu pareja de entrenamiento y rétala para entrenar juntas ⬇️👀
Nos vemos mañana para entrenar piernas y glúteos a las 8:00am EST 🔥 
Method: repite cada ejercicio 3 veces- 45seg ON - 10seg OFF

Guarda la rutina, compártela y hagámosla juntas 👊🏼
-

Need new #Glute workouts for 2020? These are 6 exercises you should be doing 🍑 Visit @SculptMobility for daily pain management, flexibility, and workout advice📚 
.
👉🏻 Marque sua parceira de treino para esse treininho sinixxxxxtro do 💪🏻🤮
.
👉🏻 Terra Sumo 10 repetições conjugado com afundo no banco 10 repetições cada perna 4 séries
👉🏻 Mesa flexora 5 séries de 10 repetições com pico de contração e descida controlada
👉🏻 Elevação pélvica com drop 4 séries de 10 com pico de contração + até a falha
👉🏻 Leg 45 unilateral com ponto zero 10 repetições cada perna + cadeira abdutora 15 repetições 4 séries
.
.
.
Credit @robertarzuniga #Fitness #fitfam #fitspo #motivation #workout #workoutvideo #legday #gym #abs
